              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "While reloading, the gun emits three jets of fog in the shape of a radiation symbol."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When firing, the gray components of the gun briefly glow green, matching the color of its lasers. The glow will still be green even if a bullet modifier changes the color of the player's bullets.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " The "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Golden",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " skin instead glows yellow."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " The "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Fr3nd",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " skin glows blue."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Unlike other starting guns, the Rogue Special does not eject brass when firing, so it cannot be used to find the path to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Planar Lead",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The internal name of the gun, "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Knav3",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is in reference to the Pilot being a "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "knave",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", meaning a dishonest or unscrupulous man."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The entry for the Rogue Special in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Physical Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " has a small doodle of the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Pilot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
