        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Flak Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Upon Casey's invisible projectile reaching the end of its range or impacting a wall, it will split into three visible high damage pellets, drastically increasing Casey's effective range. These pellets retain Caseys ability to launch killed enemies.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "These pellets do not reflect projectiles."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Enemy bullets reflected by the initial Casey swing will also be affected by Flak Bullets, splitting apart on impact."
                }
