            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "If the Composite Gun is duct taped to a different gun, it will be duct taped as two different three-shot magazines. One clip represents the uncharged shots, the other the charged shots.\n"
                }
              ],
              "sub": [
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "Firing a charged shot with this gun will fully empty the original magazine of the base gun, but will "
                    },
