  {
    "name": "Siren",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/0/0a/Siren.png",
    "notes": "Fires a blast of bubbles that leave pools of water. Negates fall damage and goop effects while equipped.",
    "quote": "Mershotgun",
    "quality": "C",
    "type": "Semiautomatic",
    "dps": "32.0",
    "magazine_size": "6",
    "ammo_capacity": "200",
    "damage": "18 (6x3)",
    "fire_rate": "0.40",
    "reload_time": "1.5",
    "shot_speed": "23",
    "range": "60",
    "force": "30",
    "spread": "0",
    "class": "SHOTGUN",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Fires a narrow spread of 3 water bullets, that burst into pools of water "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Goop",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " upon hitting an obstacle or enemy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Prevents damage from falling into pits while held."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Harmful "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Goop",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " has no affect on the player while the Siren is held. This includes "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Status effects",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " like fire or poison, as well as slow effects from "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Phaser Spider",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " web."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Battery Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Battery Bullets can electrify the puddles of water created by the Siren, creating powerful damaging puddles."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Book of Chest Anatomy",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " +  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Brave New World"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Because Book of Chest Anatomy raises the chance of broken chests dropping an item to 55%, all chests effectively have a 55% chance to drop the item they were predicted to contain when broken."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "As The Siren creates water, it is able to extinguish the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Fireplace",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Keep of the Lead Lord",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", and the fuses of fused "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Chests",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Siren is in the SHOTGUN "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Guns",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", and as such benefits from the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Shotgun Affinity"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "A Siren is a mythical creature that lures sailors to their doom, often portrayed as a mermaid."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Brave New World"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " may be a reference to the DC Comic Superhero \"Aquaman\" who rules an underwater kingdom, wields a trident as a symbol of authority, and has a prosthetic hand."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "It is also a reference to the animated Disney film \"The Little Mermaid\", as the titular mermaid Ariel trades her voice for legs, her father Poseidon wields a trident, and the fish companion summoned by the synergy resembles Ariel's companion, Flounder. Additionally, Ariel sings a song titled \"Part of Your World\", alluded to in the synergy's name, \"Brave New World\". The gun is also colored the same as Ariel, with a green bottom (stock / tail) and purple top (foregrip / bikini)."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The entry for the Siren in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Physical Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " has a small doodle of a mermaid "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bullet Kin",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", as well as a crab and fish."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
