  {
    "name": "Shotbow",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/a/a7/Shotbow.png",
    "notes": "Fires a shotgun blast of bolts.",
    "quote": "A Teleporter Accident",
    "quality": "B",
    "type": "Semiautomatic",
    "dps": "30.9",
    "magazine_size": "3",
    "ammo_capacity": "80",
    "damage": "36 (6x6)",
    "fire_rate": "1.00",
    "reload_time": "1.5",
    "shot_speed": "26",
    "range": "1,000",
    "force": "25",
    "spread": "5",
    "class": "SHOTGUN",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Shotbow is in the SHOTGUN "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Guns",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and as such benefits from the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Shotgun Affinity"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This gun's description could be a reference to the episode Tuvix, from the TV show Star Trek Voyager, where two characters were merged into one as a result of a transporter (a sort of teleporter) accident, which is itself a reference to the film The Fly."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "It could also be a reference to the short story by George Langelaan titled \"The Fly\" originally published in the June 1957 issue of Playboy magazine, which inspired two films of the same name released in "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "1958",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Fly_(1958_film)"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "1986",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Fly_(1986_film)"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", in which a scientist accidentally combines himself with a fly while attempting to invent a working teleporter.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "synref",
                  "v": "Second Accident"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " synergy is a reference to the 1986 film, as the Shotbow's appearance changes to that of one covered with fleshy growths and a pair of wings, referencing the scientist's later state."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The entry for the Shotbow in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Physical Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " has a small doodle of a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bullet Kin",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " riding on an arrow."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Triple Crossbow",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/2/24/Triple_Crossbow.png",
