                  "url": "http://combineoverwiki.net/wiki/combine"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " from Half-Life 2."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The pickup line, \"Halve lives\", is also a reference to the name of the game "
