                  "t": "ext",
                  "v": "4",
                  "url": "https://metalgear.fandom.com/wiki/Metal_Gear_Solid_4:_Guns_of_the_Patriots"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ".",
                  "style": "i"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The weapon's description is a reference to the MAC cannon from the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Halo",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Halo_(series)"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " franchise."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The weapon's charging animation in which two perpendicular beams rotate and align with a central beam is likely a reference to the railgun in the game Ruiner, also published by Devolver, which features a railgun with an identical charging animation"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The weapon's description (\"DANGER: HIGH VOLTAGE\") is likely a reference to Electric Six's single "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Danger! High Voltage",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Production Model"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - This Synergy's function is likely a reference to Destiny's Sleeper Simulant weapon (the Destiny 1 iteration, specifically), which functions with near-exact similarity along with its \"Activate IKELOS\" perk, which allows its projectile to bounce 5 times off of surfaces as well. As well as the synergy activating with "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Nanomachines",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " being a reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "SIVA",
              "url": "https://www.destinypedia.com/SIVA"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " from Destiny, which has ties to the weapon Sleeper Simulant."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The entry for the Prototype Railgun in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Physical Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " has a small doodle of what appears to be "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Otacon",
              "url": "https://metalgear.fandom.com/wiki/Hal_Emmerich"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " from the "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Metal Gear Solid",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " franchise."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
