              "t": "text",
              "v": "The quote at the end of Ammonomicon Entry is a reference to the book of "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Genesis",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genesis_creation_narrative"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
