    "notes": "Has a chance to transmogrify.",
    "quote": "Dark Arts",
    "quality": "C",
    "type": "Semiautomatic",
    "dps": "42.0",
    "magazine_size": "6",
    "ammo_capacity": "150",
    "damage": "21 (7x3)",
    "fire_rate": "0.30",
    "reload_time": "1.5",
    "shot_speed": "23",
    "range": "60",
    "force": "30",
    "spread": "5",
    "class": "SILLY",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Fires a spread of three magic projectiles that each have a 10% chance to transmogrify enemies they hit into harmless chickens.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Bosses",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " and "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Mimic",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " are immune to being transmogrified."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Transmogrification can affect enemies which are normally invulnerable, such as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gunreaper",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Lead Cube",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Despite being a shotgun, the Bundle of Wands is not in the SHOTGUN "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Guns",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", and as such does not benefit from the   "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Shotgun Affinity"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Shooting walls with the gun leaves rune-shaped indentations."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Special Delivery"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to Hedwig, the snowy owl that accompanies Harry in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Harry Potter",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " book series. In that series, owls are used to deliver mail."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Chicken Arise"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Aqua Teen Hunger Force",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " episode \"Video Ouija\", in which a witch doctor uses the same phrase."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "A unique higher resolution sprite of the Bundle of Wands appears on the opening page of the 'Guns' chapter in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Physical Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Staff of Firepower",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/7/79/Staff_of_Firepower.png",
    "notes": "Reloading alternates between a rapid fire pistol and a beam weapon that can set enemies on fire.",
    "quote": "Missing Link",
    "quality": "A",
    "type": "Semiautomatic",
    "dps": "Gun: 24 Staff: 54.3 Both: 42.3",
    "magazine_size": "Gun: 6 Staff: 12",
    "ammo_capacity": "200",
    "damage": "Gun: 7 Staff: 12",
    "fire_rate": "0.15",
    "reload_time": "1.0",
    "shot_speed": "25",
    "range": "1,000",
    "force": "12",
    "spread": "7",
    "class": "SILLY",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This gun fires faster when shot rapidly like a semi-automatic weapon, rather than holding the trigger like an automatic."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Chicken Arise"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Magic Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the chance for Staff of Firepower to transmogrify enemies and size of bullets are increased."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Special Delivery"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Owl",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the gun's and Owl's shots bounce, and Owl turns skeletal and fires letters at enemies.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "With this synergy, quickly switching between a synergy gun and a non-synergy gun will make Owl rapidly blank if bullets are near and rapidly shoot."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This synergy strangely also affects "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Baby Good Shelleton",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ", making its lasers bounce off of walls and enemies."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The beam-like bullets can be absorbed by "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gunjurer",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This gun is a reference to the Fire Rod from the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Legend of Zelda",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Legend_of_Zelda"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " series."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Chicken Arise"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a reference to Aqua Teen Hunger Force episode \"Video Ouija\", in which a witch doctor named Billywitchdoctor.com attempts to resurrect Master Shake, who had been killed earlier in the episode, by chanting \"ARISE CHICKEN, CHICKEN ARISE!!\" repeatedly."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
