            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Silver Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "), will on occasion shoot a bullet with extremely high damage, being able to instantly kill any enemy or boss."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "  Possible Bug The special UI icon for both the Phoenix and  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Phoenix Up"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " in the "
