            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ". Tetsuo similarly possesses a bionic arm, and famously undergoes extreme and disturbing mutations. The synergy's name, \"Neo Tech, Yo\" also seems to allude to Neotokyo, the setting where the story takes place."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
