  {
    "name": "Proton Backpack",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/b/b0/Proton_Backpack.png",
    "notes": "Fires a continuous, slow-moving, homing stream.",
    "quote": "Crossing Streams",
    "quality": "B",
    "type": "Beam",
    "dps": "50.0",
    "magazine_size": "500",
    "ammo_capacity": "500",
    "damage": "50/s",
    "fire_rate": "0.10",
    "reload_time": "N/A",
    "shot_speed": "14",
    "range": "90",
    "force": "30",
    "spread": "0",
    "class": "BEAM",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Electron Pack"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Zombie Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Ghost Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", kills with the Proton Backpack spawn "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gunslinger's Ashes",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " ghosts that attack enemies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The lock-on feature makes the gun ideal for bosses and strong mobs."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This gun is a reference to the anti-ghost weapon from the movie "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Ghostbusters",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghostbusters"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ".\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The tagline is a reference to the one of the movie's most famous phrases, \"Don't cross the streams\"."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The \"something strange\" mentioned in the Ammonomicon entry is a nod to the Ghostbusters theme song which asks, \"When there's something strange in the neighborhood, who ya gonna call?\""
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The \"team of investigators\" is presumed to have been the Ghostbusters themselves."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Electron Pack"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is most likely a reference to the Wunderwaffe DG-2 from the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Call of Duty",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Call_of_Duty:_Black_Ops"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Franchise."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The shape of the Proton Backpack in the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Electron Pack"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Is similar to the shape of the Blood launcher from Nuclear throne"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Mega Douser",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/c/c1/Mega_Douser.png",
    "notes": "Fires a continuous stream of water that leaves water puddles on floor.",
    "quote": "Contents Under Pressure",
    "quality": "D",
    "type": "Beam",
    "dps": "15.0",
    "magazine_size": "900",
    "ammo_capacity": "900",
    "damage": "15/s",
    "fire_rate": "0.10",
    "reload_time": "N/A",
    "shot_speed": "20",
    "range": "20",
    "force": "40",
    "spread": "0",
    "class": "BEAM",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This water stream can extinguish the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Fireplace",
