            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " fuses, and clean off hidden Rainbow Chests."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Because this water stream deals WATER type damage, it does not ignite "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Coaler",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", and deals double damage to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Muzzle Wisp",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Muzzle Flare",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Battery Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shock Rifle",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Can electrify the water left by the Mega Douser, dealing a considerable amount of damage to enemies that stand on it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bouncy Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - The stream of water bounces numerous times fragmenting and splattering around the room. This usually covers most of the room in water."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The name and appearance of the gun reference "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Super Soaker",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Super_Soaker"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", a brand of toy water guns.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "More specifically, its shape and color scheme are based on the original "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ext",
                  "v": "Super Soaker 50",
                  "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Super_Soaker_50"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "synref",
                  "v": "Hydro Pump"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " synergy is a reference to the Pokémon move of the same name. This is likely due to "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Escape Rope",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " also being a reference to an item in the Pokémon series."
                }
              ]
            }
