                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The gun itself as well as its flavor text are a reference to the idiom \"Like shooting fish in a barrel\" describing an effortless or simple action, with guaranteed success."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "One Fish Two Fish"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Is a clear reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "a book of a similar name",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/One_Fish,_Two_Fish,_Red_Fish,_Blue_Fish"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " written by Dr. Seuss."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This gun's quote in Portuguese, \"Isso, Isso, Isso\", is a reference to a popular Mexican TV show called "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "El Chavo del Ocho",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/El_Chavo_del_Ocho"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " about a boy who lives in a barrel."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Trick Gun",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/d/d1/Trick_Gun.png",
    "notes": "Reloading transforms the gun between a pistol and a shotgun.",
    "quote": "Reload To Transform",
    "quality": "C",
    "type": "Semiautomatic",
    "dps": "16.5",
    "magazine_size": "6",
    "ammo_capacity": "200",
    "damage": "Pistol: 7 Shotgun: 16 (2x8)",
    "fire_rate": "0.10 (pistol) 0.80 (shotgun)",
    "reload_time": "1.2",
    "shot_speed": "30 (pistol) 25 (shotgun)",
    "range": "60 (pistol) 12 (shotgun)",
    "force": "11 (pistol) 5 (shotgun)",
    "spread": "2 (pistol) 10 (shotgun)",
    "class": "SILLY",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Trick Gun can be reloaded without changing its form by switching to another gun, waiting approximately twice the amount of time it takes to reload normally, than switching back."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Fear the Old Blood"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Blood Brooch",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bloody Eye",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Rolling Eye",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", reload time is decreased by 33% and fire rate is increased by 20%."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Hell Singing"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Silver Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", Trick Gun will deal an extra 50% damage to jammed enemies for a total of 487.5% damage."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Insight"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Huntsman",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", a creature appears at entrances to secret rooms, revealing their location."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If the player drops the Trick gun in shotgun form, it will transform back into a pistol when picked up again."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This gun is a reference to the transforming trick weapons from "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Bloodborne",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bloodborne"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The two main types of hunter firearms in Bloodborne are the pistol and the blunderbuss, the same two weapons the Trick Gun transforms into."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Demon Hunter is both a reference to the main character in Bloodborne being a Hunter, and a reference to the first game in the whole series that came from Bloodborne, "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Demon's Souls",
              "url": "https://demonssouls.wiki.fextralife.com/Demons+Souls+Wiki"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", in which you hunt down demons to take their souls."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Hell Singing"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a likely reference to the fictional hunter "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Van Helsing",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abraham_Van_Helsing"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Insight"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Bloodborne",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bloodborne"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", wherein Insight is a mechanic that gradually lets one see things that are beyond perception."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The creature from the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Insight"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy strangely resembles the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Interdimensional Horror",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", potentially meaning they are from the same species."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Fear the Old Blood"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Bloodborne",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bloodborne"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", where the old blood refers to the blood of the Great Ones."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If Duct Taped with another gun, it will only Duct Tape to one of the gun's forms."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Mailbox",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/8/88/Mailbox.png",
    "notes": "Fires mail at enemies. The last bullet of each magazine is a package, which can explode, leave confetti, burn , or poison .",
