                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " (which, despite their name, generally take the form of boxes)."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The option of a box which leaves poison is likely a reference to "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ext",
                  "v": "ricin letter incidents",
                  "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2003_ricin_letters"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "."
