            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Unity",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", hitting an enemy with Trashcannon causes it and its bullets to briefly freeze. Bullets slow down to a very low percentage of its original travel speed, having a very slight amount of motion."
