              "v": "Jumping... is useless"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", it will only create 5 Quad Laser shots. This can be circumvented by dropping Moonscraper, using an active while holding Quad Laser, then picking Moonscraper back up. This causes the tons of Quad Laser shots to suddenly gain lasers, flooding the entire area with beams."
