              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Great Queen Ant"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to Earthworm Jim, specifically "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "The Evil Queen Pulsating, Bloated, Festering, Sweaty, Pus-filled, Malformed, Slug-for-a-Butt",
