            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bouncy Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Each additional time the original Banana bounces, it will create two more sub-bananas. Because bouncy bullets adds two additional shot bounces, it raises the number of total sub-bananas per shot from 4 to 8."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
