    "range": "1,000",
    "force": "8",
    "spread": "35",
    "class": "FULLAUTO",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Shredder"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Metronome",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", spread is doubled, decreasing accuracy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Prior to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Supply Drop Update",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the arrows did not home in on enemies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If all arrows land on enemies, this gun deals very high damage per second. However, without accuracy upgrades, this will be nigh impossible to do even on relatively large enemies without getting dangerously close to them.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "It does make a good weapon for dealing with large crowds of enemies."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This is a reference to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Guzheng",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guzheng"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", a Chinese traditional plucked musical string instrument.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "More specifically, the quote "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Hustle",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " and this gun's method of attack are a reference to the sword-shooting Guzheng from "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ext",
                  "v": "Kung Fu Hustle",
                  "url": "https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0373074/"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "\"zh\" should be pronounced as \"g\" in gentle, making a name a pun on \"Gungeon\"."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
